 BLUSRVSP {
  coords 1904.224 0 9504.53
  m_sTitle "Service & Support"
  m_sTextData "- There is a ammo crate at spawn with a bunch of supplies."\
  "After we have destroyed three caches, a 2nd ammo crate will be delivered to spawn."\
  ""\
  "- Within the garage where the Humvees are located is a crate with a mix of humvee ammo, fuel, and repair kits."\
  ""\
  "- We currently have 20x tickets in the team pool."\
  "For each cache destroyed, we'll recieve 5 tickets to the pool."\
  "Individual users are not limited to how many tickets each person can use from the pool. We'll spawn where we started."\
  "(THERE IS NO WAY TO TRACK USED TICKETS, YOU BETTER KEEP COUNT OR SOMETHING IDK)"\
  ""\
  ""
  m_aVisibleForFactions {
   "RHS_USAF"
  }
  m_iOrder 5
 }
